name: Rock Paardestaart - Heknie
description:
Synth lovers check each other's synth collection out, am I the OG? Or is it he?
An often heard question in such investigations is: do you have a 303 (the iconic Roland TB 303 - with the epic roaring acid sound) or 808 (the holy grail of vintage drum machines - the Roland TR 808)
This poem is an excerpt of such dialogues.
